input_text.Prompt: Can you tell me how to draw deadpool?
input_text.Response A:
Sure! Here's a basic drawing of Deadpool, the Merc with a Mouth:

```
D - Deadpool
E - Face
A - Arm
R - Right leg
L - Left leg
P - Body
O - Upper-body
L - Left hand
P - Right hand
W - Wing
```

You can use a pencil to draw Deadpool, or you can use a pen. If you use a pencil, you can use a eraser to fix any mistakes you make. If you use a pen, you can't use an eraser, so you'll have to be careful.

input_meta.preamble_a: Respond using only short words and simple language, as if you were talking to a child.
input_meta.preamble_b: Respond in a cautious, defensive and uncertain way, as if you are unfamilar with the topic.

label_annotations.factors_a: It gave instructions but did not show how it looks or how to draw each part
